{
  "source_id": "sage",
  "entity_id": "sage-intacct-vendor",
  "mapping_version": "v1",
  "_comment": [
    "Canonical mapping for Sage Intacct accounts-payable/vendor object.",
    "",
    "Vendors are AP counterparts to AR customers.  They do not participate in",
    "the 'company' entity resolution workflow in Phase 5 (Intacct only).  A",
    "separate 'supplier' entity type is tracked for Phase 6.",
    "",
    "PK: 'id' (Intacct vendor code) mapped to 'vendor_id'.",
    "No entity resolution integration yet — this is raw-to-curated only."
  ],
  "rules": [
    {
